                <summary>Article calls attention to Harris's "fishy" non-advocacy of
                Letcher.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Who is to Blame?</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Lambastes post office for allowing portions of subscribers' papers to
                    disappear.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
