                        <fn>William L.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Letcher and Goggin will go after each other in Charlottesville next
                Monday.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Post Office Affairs in Virginia</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Richmond Whig article criticizes Virginia post office for being corrupt and
                    for allowing Opposition political documents to circulate pre-paid. The
                    Vindicator denounces the Whig's assertions by citing lack of evidence.</summary>
            </div>
