                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Senator</pf>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Sandidge</ln>
                        <fn>John M.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Benjamin</ln>
                        <fn/>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Mr.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Senator Clay praised John Letcher in a speech, declaring that if Letcher
                    should be beaten, the party would be broken in the South and West.</summary>
            </div>
